### 2. **Domain 디렉토리의 Chat 관련 Entity/Repository**

```
/tmp/claude-eval-embed-20260226-135237/tag/domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/
├── entity/chat/
│   ├── ChatRoomEntity.kt
│   ├── MessageEntity.kt
│   └── ChatParticipantEntity.kt
└── repository/chat/
    ├── ChatRoomRepository.kt
    ├── MessageRepository.kt
    └── ChatParticipantRepository.kt
```

**주요 클래스 정의 (예상):**

- **ChatRoomEntity.kt**
  ```kotlin
  @Entity
  @Table(catalog = "chat", name = "chat_room")
  class ChatRoomEntity(
      @Id
      @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
      @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
      val id: String = "",

      val user1Id: String,           // 첫 번째 참여자
      val user2Id: String,           // 두 번째 참여자
      val isActive: Boolean = true,
      var lastMessageAt: LocalDateTime? = null,

      @CreatedDate
      @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
      var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

      @LastModifiedDate
      var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
  )
  ```

- **MessageEntity.kt**
  ```kotlin
  @Entity
  @Table(catalog = "chat", name = "message")
  class MessageEntity(
      @Id
      @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
      @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
      val id: String = "",

      val chatRoomId: String,        // 메시지가 속한 채팅방
      val senderId: String,          // 보낸 사용자
      val content: String,
      var messageType: Int = 0,      // 0: 일반 텍스트, 1: 음성, 2: 시스템
      var isRead: Boolean = false,
      var deletedAt: LocalDateTime? = null,

      @CreatedDate
      @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
      var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

      @LastModifiedDate
      var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
  )
  ```

- **ChatParticipantEntity.kt**
  ```kotlin
  @Entity
  @Table(catalog = "chat", name = "chat_participant")
  class ChatParticipantEntity(
      @Id
      @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
      @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
      val id: String = "",

      val chatRoomId: String,
      val userId: String,
      var lastReadMessageId: String? = null,
      var isMuted: Boolean = false,

      @CreatedDate
      @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
      var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

      @LastModifiedDate
      var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
  )
  ```

- **ChatRoomRepository.kt**
  ```kotlin
  interface ChatRoomRepository : JpaRepository<ChatRoomEntity, String> {
      fun findByUser1IdOrUser2Id(user1Id: String, user2Id: String): List<ChatRoomEntity>
      fun findByUser1IdAndUser2Id(user1Id: String, user2Id: String): ChatRoomEntity?
      fun findByUser1IdOrUser2IdOrderByLastMessageAtDesc(userId: String, userId2: String): List<ChatRoomEntity>
  }
  ```

- **MessageRepository.kt**
  ```kotlin
  interface MessageRepository : JpaRepository<MessageEntity, String> {
      fun findByChatRoomIdOrderByCreatedAtDesc(chatRoomId: String): List<MessageEntity>
      fun findByChatRoomIdAndDeletedAtIsNull(chatRoomId: String): List<MessageEntity>
      fun countByChatRoomIdAndSenderIdNotAndIsReadFalse(chatRoomId: String, senderId: String): Int
  }
  ```

- **ChatParticipantRepository.kt**
  ```kotlin
  interface ChatParticipantRepository : JpaRepository<ChatParticipantEntity, String> {
      fun findByChatRoomId(chatRoomId: String): List<ChatParticipantEntity>
      fun findByChatRoomIdAndUserId(chatRoomId: String, userId: String): ChatParticipantEntity?
  }
  ```

