### 4. **GraphQL 모듈의 Chat 관련 파일**

```
/tmp/claude-eval-embed-20260226-135237/tag/graphql/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/
├── controller/chat/
│   └── ChatController.kt              (GraphQL Query/Mutation 처리)
├── service/chat/
│   └── ChatService.kt                 (gRPC Client)
└── resources/graphql/
    └── chat/
        └── schema.graphqls            (GraphQL 스키마)
```

- **schema.graphqls**
  ```graphql
  type ChatRoom {
    id: ID!
    user1: SimpleUser!
    user2: SimpleUser!
    isActive: Boolean!
    lastMessage: Message
    lastMessageAt: String
    createdAt: String!
    updatedAt: String!
  }

  type Message {
    id: ID!
    chatRoom: ChatRoom!
    sender: SimpleUser!
    content: String!
    messageType: Int!
    isRead: Boolean!
    createdAt: String!
  }

  input CreateChatRoomInput {
    otherUserId: String!
  }

  input SendMessageInput {
    roomId: String!
    content: String!
    messageType: Int
  }

  extend type Query {
    chatRoom(roomId: ID!): ChatRoom
    chatRooms(limit: Int, offset: Int): [ChatRoom!]!
    messages(roomId: ID!, limit: Int, offset: Int): [Message!]!
  }

  extend type Mutation {
    createChatRoom(input: CreateChatRoomInput!): ChatRoom!
    sendMessage(input: SendMessageInput!): Message!
    markAsRead(roomId: ID!, messageId: ID!): Boolean!
  }
  ```

- **ChatController.kt**
  ```kotlin
  @Controller
  class ChatController(
      private val chatService: ChatService,
      private val userService: UserService,
  ) {
      @QueryMapping
      @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
      fun chatRoom(
          @UserId userId: String,
          @Argument roomId: ID,
      ): ChatRoomResponse? { ... }

      @QueryMapping
      @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
      fun chatRooms(
          @UserId userId: String,
          @Argument limit: Int?,
          @Argument offset: Int?,
      ): List<ChatRoomResponse> { ... }

      @QueryMapping
      @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
      fun messages(
          @UserId userId: String,
          @Argument roomId: ID,
          @Argument limit: Int?,
          @Argument offset: Int?,
      ): List<MessageResponse> { ... }

      @MutationMapping
      @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
      fun createChatRoom(
          @UserId userId: String,
          @Argument input: CreateChatRoomInput,
      ): ChatRoomResponse { ... }

      @MutationMapping
      @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
      fun sendMessage(
          @UserId userId: String,
          @Argument input: SendMessageInput,
      ): MessageResponse { ... }

      @MutationMapping
      @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
      fun markAsRead(
          @UserId userId: String,
          @Argument roomId: ID,
          @Argument messageId: ID,
      ): Boolean { ... }
  }
  ```

- **ChatService.kt** (GraphQL 모듈)
  ```kotlin
  @Service
  class ChatService {
      @GrpcClient("chat-grpc")
      private lateinit var stub: ChatServiceGrpc.ChatServiceBlockingStub

      fun createChatRoom(userId: String, otherUserId: String): CreateChatRoomResponse { ... }
      fun getChatRoom(roomId: String): GetChatRoomResponse { ... }
      fun listChatRooms(userId: String, limit: Int, offset: Int): ListChatRoomsResponse { ... }
      fun sendMessage(roomId: String, userId: String, content: String, messageType: Int): SendMessageResponse { ... }
      fun listMessages(roomId: String, limit: Int, offset: Int): ListMessagesResponse { ... }
      fun markAsRead(roomId: String, userId: String, messageId: String): MarkAsReadResponse { ... }
  }
  ```

